User
    ident Text
    password Text Maybe
    familyName Text
    givenName Text

    UniqueUser ident
    deriving Typeable

Issue
    subject Text
    description Text Maybe

    limitdate Day Maybe

    opener UserId
    created UTCTime default=now()
    updated UTCTime default=now()

Channel
    type     Logic
    issue    IssueId

Ticket
    channel  ChannelId
    domain   UserId
    codomain UserId
    assign   UserId

    created UTCTime default=now()
    updated UTCTime default=now()

Comment
    channel ChannelId
    comment Text
    speaker UserId

    created UTCTime default=now()
    updated UTCTime default=now()

 -- By default this file is used in Model.hs (which is imported by Foundation.hs)
